            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1d4eb787d6f4506e-f09fcd twpub-1d4eb787d6f4506e-6b4cd0\"><p>1.F.4.  Except for the limited right of replacement or refund set forth\nin paragraph 1.F.3, this work is provided to you 'AS-IS' WITH NO OTHER\nWARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO\nWARRANTIES OF MERCHANTIBILITY OR FITNESS FOR ANY PURPOSE.</p></div>"
